The recommendation covers all areas of interest:
🔹 Trade
🔹 Judicial cooperation
🔹 Foreign policy
🔹 Security
🔹 Participation in EU programmes
and more.
#NewBeginnings 🇪🇺🇬🇧

We have issued a recommendation to the Council to open negotiations on a new partnership with the United Kingdom. 
It is based on existing European Council guidelines as well as on the EU-UK Political Declaration from October 2019.

It's vital we act.
